adin could outdamage 4 level 30 players and a warder. When the mob went down I got the exp and the loot. Since I had brought the BL just to get the drop I let the group know that I was going to take it. (fabled gloves of the magi, ac 9 summoning efficency 2) I offered to buff them back up and help with the fabled undead knight as I already had that drop, but they left instead. <br />I dont feel bad, or that I was rude. They needed the help, asked for it and no one was more suprised than I, that I got the exp. <br /><br /></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />For Truth, Justice, and the Norrathian Way!</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from East Coast</td></tr></table>
